	</script></div><div class="sliderWrap"><ul class="slides"><li style="width: 100%; float: left; margin-right: -100%; position: relative; display: none;"><div style="position: absolute; background-color: black; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; opacity: 0.5;"></div><div class="slider-text"><h1>NSF Project Outcomes Report<br/></h1><p><a href="page/nsf-project-outcomes-report.html">Epicenter's project outcomes report documents the activities and impact of the center from 2011 to 2016. <i class="fa fa-chevron-circle-right"></i></a></p></div><img src="images/12321%3Bjsessionid=801206EC6C7B1397C92EE10BBB9E6959.jpeg" class="sliderImageCaman"/></li><li style="width: 100%; float: left; margin-right: -100%; position: relative; display: none;"><div style="position: absolute; background-color: black; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; opacity: 0.5;"></div><div class="slider-text"><h1>About Epicenter<br/></h1><p><a href="page/about-programs.html">Epicenter was funded by the NSF from 2011 to 2016 to help faculty, students and academic leaders support entrepreneurship and innovation learning in undergraduate engineering education. <i class="fa fa-chevron-circle-right"></i></a></p></div><img src="images/11711%3Bjsessionid=801206EC6C7B1397C92EE10BBB9E6959.jpeg" class="sliderImageCaman"/></li><li style="width: 100%; float: left; margin-right: -100%; position: relative; display: none;"><div style="position: absolute; background-color: black; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; opacity: 0.5;"></div><div class="slider-text"><h1>University Innovation Fellows<br/></h1><p><a href="page/university-innovation-fellows.html">This program empowered engineering students and their peers to become change agents at their schools.  <i class="fa fa-chevron-circle-right"></i></a></p></div><img src="images/11681%3Bjsessionid=801206EC6C7B1397C92EE10BBB9E6959.jpeg" class="sliderImageCaman"/></li><li style="width: 100%; float: left; margin-right: -100%; position: relative; display: none;"><div style="position: absolute; background-color: black; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; opacity: 0.5;"></div><div class="slider-text"><h1>Pathways to Innovation Program<br/></h1><p><a href="page/pathways-to-innovation.html">Pathways helped faculty teams incorporate innovation and entrepreneurship into undergraduate engineering education.  <i class="fa fa-chevron-circle-right"></i></a></p></div><img src="images/11701%3Bjsessionid=801206EC6C7B1397C92EE10BBB9E6959.jpeg" class="sliderImageCaman"/></li><li style="width: 100%; float: left; margin-right: -100%; position: relative; display: none;"><div style="position: absolute; background-color: black; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; opacity: 0.5;"></div><div class="slider-text"><h1>Fostering Innovative Generations Studies<br/></h1><p><a href="page/fostering-innovative-generations-studies.html">Learn about the Epicenter research team's papers and activities, including the national Engineering Majors Survey. <i class="fa fa-chevron-circle-right"></i></a></p></div><img src="images/10671%3Bjsessionid=801206EC6C7B1397C92EE10BBB9E6959.jpeg" class="sliderImageCaman"/></li></ul></div><div class="homeAbout"><div class="intro"><h2>About Epicenter</h2><p>Epicenter was funded by the <a target="_blank" href="http://www.nsf.gov/">National Science Foundation</a> from 2011 to 2016 and directed by <a target="_blank" href="http://www.stanford.edu/">Stanford University</a> and <a target="_blank" href="http://www.venturewell.org/">VentureWell</a>. Epicenter's mission was to empower U.S. undergraduate engineering students to bring their ideas to life for the benefit of our economy and society.</p><a class="btn" href="page/about.html">Learn More <i class="fa fa-chevron-right"></i></a></div></div><div class="main"><div class="programs">
